      <p>"There are several great Forges in the kingdom. The <strong>People's Forge</strong> (GitHub) is the most popular - that's where most Archivists of the world gather. The <strong>Autonomous Forge</strong> (GitLab) lets you build your own independent forge. The <strong>Atlassian Forge</strong> (Bitbucket) integrates perfectly with the management tools of the great guilds. Choose your forge according to your needs, but <strong>learn at least one thoroughly</strong>."</p>
