      <p>The Master Archivist places a hand on your shoulder.</p>
      <p>"You have just completed your <strong>first shipment to the Forges</strong>. Your scrolls are now safe, duplicated and accessible from any outpost in the kingdom. This is the foundation of everything that follows."</p>
